{"tid":58013,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 誓 要 搣 甩 豬 腩 肉","createTime":"2016-12-28T13:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T20:12:34.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb7fe4e4b8afbcba6eb2433c15737468251e563c","tid":58013,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"吳業坤 (坤哥 ) 去年憑一曲〈原來她不夠愛我〉，橫掃各大頒獎禮成為大贏家，不單身價急升，連帶身形都一併膨脹！於是無綫與唱片公司下令極速瘦身，向來唔注重外表的坤哥不敢怠慢，最近找了健身教練幫拖。但係佢本身體虛又虧，往往未能達標，教練都無哂佢乎。日前本刊記者目擊仍然豬腩肉隨身的坤哥喺健身房地獄式減肥，可見佢上氣唔接下氣，個樣仲極度痛苦，慘過台慶做隻棋！<br />\n<br />\n今年26歲的坤哥，以四眼仔毒男形象見稱，去年憑一首歌成功越級揮低陳奕迅，在頒奬禮上擸盡歌曲大獎，更以僅出過兩張碟而能登上歌手們的終極目標，8月在紅館舉行演唱會。坤哥人紅收入升，吸金力強，吸脂力更勁，腰間豬腩肉凸現，上載至社交媒體的相片也要遮去豬腩肉才貼出來。早前他拍攝劇集《殭》要赤裸上身，豬腩肉現形，相當嚇人﹗<br />\n<br />\n眼見坤哥近排肥左成個碼，唱片公司都睇唔過眼，命令佢喺頒獎禮前減肥，告別毒男形象。日前坤哥收工即到北角健身房，換上背心短打，拉筋後就開始做不同器械。坤哥以一雙鬆泡泡手臂，用盡洪荒之力都只喺將器械推前兩小步。教練最初不停看錶出聲鞭策，唔俾坤哥暫停，之不過坤哥多次未能完成教練要求。<br />\n<br />\n雖然坤哥對外形唔嗲唔吊，但對獎項絕對着緊，近日更親自到不到電台派歌，知情者爆：「雖然唱片公司有人會去電台，但坤哥堅持親自去，商台仲連續去咗幾日，佢舊年攞咗我最喜愛歌曲，梗係想冧莊啦。」但坤哥今時唔同往日，不單要出席各大頒獎禮，又在新劇擔任劇份重的角色，唔努力減肥點得！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/dad_1883805701585cf81e369ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fdad_1883805701585cf81e369ef.jpg&h=310d73db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/42-1024x639_127744225585cf52e65ea3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F42-1024x639_127744225585cf52e65ea3.png&h=ba9a13c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/52-1024x625_372551152585cf532cbc6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F52-1024x625_372551152585cf532cbc6b.png&h=9d64935b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a06852936bd44639d39158161d474788f54e961","tid":58013,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔想知"},{"pid":"381c5939b30cca235e822ac7e09254efc37d349b","tid":58013,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8919f0c5185d5c6c146daa8cf57528be96a0afdf","tid":58013,"uid":61077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n眼見坤哥近排肥左成個碼，唱片公司都睇唔過眼，命令佢喺頒獎禮前減肥，告別毒男形象。日前坤哥收工即到北角健身房，換上背心短打，拉筋後就開始做不同器械。坤哥以一雙鬆泡泡手臂，用盡洪荒之力都只喺將器械推前兩小步。教練最初不停看錶出聲鞭策，唔俾坤哥暫停，之不過坤哥<span style=\"color: red;\">多次未能完成教練要求</span>。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5122ecfa5746ecee364f265398af96c13ccd0560","tid":58013,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"揮低陳奕迅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=